{"tid":2513594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"31歲男打科興左臂掹唔甩針筒送院救治 打BioNTech連續2日多科興逾2倍","createTime":"2021-05-02T15:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T15:54:05.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2c27819347bd10098d847417492d180901ec9b","tid":2513594,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"本港接種COVID-19疫苗後送院的不適「症狀」，再添奇怪新例。據了解，一名31歲男子5月1日早上在香港中央圖書館社區疫苗接種中心打首劑中國科興滅活疫苗後，因左臂「未能移除針筒」，到律敦治醫院後，醫護才能為他拔除。另外，5月2日多28,800人打德國BioNTech復必泰mRNA疫苗，較科興僅8,600人多逾2倍，這破紀錄差距連續2日沒收窄。<br />\n<br />\nCOVID-19疫苗接種計劃至5月2日已踏入第66日，約1,491,900劑已被接種。當中約952,100人打第1劑，包括約438,800人打科興，約513,300人打復必泰。約539,800人打第2劑，包括約320,100人打科興，約219,600人打復必泰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/6G3KLEW3LZGBTKAOFUMAPEZ3Y4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Rh4idfxWYAPqc2UPZsg85cDThVihWiBEGZBcHD6g2dDFUyH4SBQvedTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F6G3KLEW3LZGBTKAOFUMAPEZ3Y4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Rh4idfxWYAPqc2UPZsg85cDThVihWiBEGZBcHD6g2dDFUyH4SBQvedTg&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=0e3abad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F6G3KLEW3LZGBTKAOFUMAPEZ3Y4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Rh4idfxWYAPqc2UPZsg85cDThVihWiBEGZBcHD6g2dDFUyH4SBQvedTg&h=eeb954b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/6G3KLEW3LZGBTKAOFUMAPEZ3Y4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Rh4idfxWYAPqc2UPZsg85cDThVihWiBEGZBcHD6g2dDFUyH4SBQvedTg</a>"},{"pid":"da4c8757f